\id 1TH - Mangga Buang NT [mmo] -Papua New Guinea 1981 (web 2014)
\h 1 Tesalonika
\toc1 Pol-ate kaapiya nyendoos la vu hil bel-ate vu Tesalonika
\toc2 1 Tesalonika
\toc3 1Te
\mt1 Pol-ate kaapiya nyendoos la vu hil bel-ate vu Tesalonika
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 + o 1:1 Sin 17:1-10; 2Tes 1:1*Sa Pol-ande Silvenes ayuuh Timoti, waay kaavu kaapiyaa-jo laas vu ham bel-ato vu Tesalonika
\p sen ham atu Aamangg Anutu yuuh Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi-te hil lung laa-to. Om waay aawiingin nambe Anutu yuuh Noow lambiing samu samu naas vu ham, osin yuuh lambiing-ambe ham alompayo nanjip melaas.
\s1 Hil Tesalonika lawii-having niwêêk-ambe dando nivasa
\p 
\v 2 + o 1:2 Pil 1:3-4; Kol 1:3; 2Tes 1:11*Waay naapêêlis vu Anutu in ham pin, tonde waay akangg navu ham hôôk lohakin nalak busin pin.
\p 
\v 3 + o 1:3 1Ko 13:13; Kol 1:4-6*Hey akangg navu ham-ambe hey naalohak vu yate Aamangg Anutu in nambe ham awii-having Yesu be ham nawiing kul anivasa, tombe ham ahem naving Omaaho Bop ondeey ham nawiing kul bopaata, tonde ham akam navu yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi lôôt in nambe navu nom vu yiiy-ato.
\p 
\v 4 Halingg-aso, Anutu ahe having ham om hey alak ni nambe yoo holin ham ak.
\v 5 + o 1:5 1Ko 2:4-5; 4:20*In banye nivasa sen hey hako laas vu ham-ato, ond hey-ame aanêêl vakasin malis amu le, nganjo Vavi Vaambuung vu niwêêk vu hey-ambe ham alak ni vanuh nambe hey aanêêl vakasin keen. Tonde va pin sen hey nando having ham-ambe hey naawiing-ato, ond yik hey naawiing in nambe dôôvu ham, tombe ham ahe be ham alak ni.
\v 6 + o 1:6 1Ko 4:16; 2Tes 3:9; Sin 17:5-9*Tombe ham taamuyin va sen hey naawiing-ato osin ham navu taamuyin Omaaho Bop having, de sen ham hako banye nivasa lak-ato ond ham hako nimeen ngeeyaata, lemu Vavi Vaambuung wiing-ambe ham ahem anivasa having.
\v 7 + o 1:7 1Pi 5:3*Tombe ham kaandu hil pin sen lawii-having Yesu vu Makedonia yuuh Akaiaa-to, tombe mem layi be davu sapa hôôk ham.
\v 8 + o 1:8 Lom 1:8*In ham anêêl Omaaho Bop-ate vakasin la lohvu taaku pin. Ham-ame yoo anêêl vu Makedonia yuuh Akaia mu le, nganjo hil vu taaku pin lango banye lung la nambe ham awii-having Anutu, om hey-ame aalohvu nambe naanêêl ham taato vu omaaho ti le, in lalak ni lung la.
\v 9 + o 1:9 Sin 14:15*In hil vu taaku pin datulin vakasin lak hey nambe hey alaas vu ham atombe ham havuuh anutu tatuhin vaha-so la, de ham ahilin ham vasa vu Anutu, tombe ham atu Anutu keen sen nando metumin-ato yite hil kul vaha.
\v 10 + o 1:10 Tit 2:13; Sin 17:31; 1Tes 5:9*Tonde datulin having nambe ham monanggin Anutu Noow in nambe le nom vu baandoni, yik Yesu sen Anutu wiing-ambe kandi lak vu hil yimbin-atêêto, tonde lôôh yiiy vêêl in nipaya nyevahaan sen Anutu le bu vu omaahonôôn vu
\p taamusin-ato.
\c 2
\s1 Kul sen Pol nawiing vu Tesalonikaa-to
\p 
\v 1 + o 2:1 1Tes 1:5,9*Halingg-aso, ham oo alak ni nambe hey alaas vu ham atombe heyate kul-ame la malis amu le.
\v 2 + o 2:2 Sin 16:19-24; 17:1-9*Tonde ham alak ni nambe hey ala Pilipai munggin atombe hil lavu nivaane vu hey-ande lanêêl hey pale. Tonde hey alaas vu ham atombe hamate hil ngeeyaata layiis ngaamong vu hey having, le ma de yate Anutu vu niwêêk vu hey, om hey aanêêl Anutu-te banye nivasa langaah vu ham-ande hey-ame aayêênin e.
\v 3 De hey aanêêl vakasin vu ham in nambe ham ambiing gaving banye nivasaa-ju, ond hey-ame aanêêl vakasin ti la paya le, de hey alonggpayo me-ningook e, tonde hey-ame aawiingin nambe tatuhin ham e, malis.
\v 4 + o 2:4 1Ti 1:11; Gal 1:10; Jer 11:20*Nganjo Anutu sahi hey-ambe yi nambe hey aalohvu, tombe vu banye nivasa vu hey, om hey-ame naanêêl langaah in nambe omaahonôôn lanji hey nivasa le, nganjo hey naanêêl in nambe Anutu sen yoo nalak hey alonggpayo nii-to ji hey nivasa.
\v 5 + o 2:5 Sin 20:33; 2Pi 2:3; Lom 1:9; 1Tes 2:10*Ham alak ni lung la nambe hey oo nando having ham bôôy-ato, ond hey-ame aanêêl vakasin osin nanyêên hôôk ham alompayo in nambe ham ahem anivasa vu hey e, de Anutu nayi
\p having nambe hey-ame naavun mengg nôôn hôôk vakasin anivasaa-jo le, malis lôôt.
\v 6 + o 2:6 Jon 5:41,44*De hey-ame aawiingin nambe ham me hil vaalu gako hey haalengg jak e.
\v 7 De Kalisi-te sinaale-so hey, om lohvu hey naanêêl-ambe ham gako hey haalengg jak, le ma de hey aawiing va melaas amu vu ham lohvu vêêh ti sen nanggin yite noondin anivasaa-to.
\v 8 Hey akangg wiingin ham ondeey hey aanêêl Anutu-te banye nivasa vu ham. Le me-manyinjo mu le, nganjo hey akangg vu nambe hey aanggimb in hey aandôôvu ham ond lung, in hey ahengg having ham lôôt.
\p 
\v 9 + o 2:9 Sin 20:34; 1Ko 4:12*Om halingg-aso, ham oo alak ni lung la nambe bôôy sen hey alaas naanêêl Anutu-te banye nivasa vu ham-ato, ond hey aawiing kul bopaata lôôt in vanôôn ayuuh ame busin-ande langaah, de hey-ame navu sawaah daka le, in nambe hey-ame aambu kul bop vu ham in ham ganggin hey in vanôôn ayuuh ame le.
\v 10 Tombe ham ahe be ham alak ni, de Anutu lak ni having nambe hey aawiing va nivasa vasa osin va nivalok vu ham sen ham awii-having-ato, de hey-ame aawiing vati paya le.
\v 11 + o 2:11 Sin 20:31*Tonde ham alak ni nambe hey nanggin ham pin lohvu omaaho ti nanggin noondin-ato,
\v 12 + o 2:12 Pil 1:27; 1Pi 5:10*om hey aanêêl tanasin vu ham in nambe ham sapa dôôk mopaatôôv anivalok. Tonde hey kaandu ham-ambe hey aanêêl niwêêk vu ham nambe ham ambiing va pin nohvu Anutu ka, in yoo holin ham in nambe ham andukanaam gaving yite hil-ambe ganggin ham, be mem ham naatu yite hil anikaapulis-ate.
\s1 Lawii-having keen om daale niwêêk-ambe daaku nimeen
\p 
\v 13 + o 2:13 1Tes 1:2; 2Tes 2:13; Gal 1:11-12*Yik hey naapêêlis nala vu Anutu nalak busin pin in vati having nambe hey aanêêl vakasin-anjo vu ham atombe ham hango nambe Anutu-te vakasin, tombe ham hako lak-ambe ham anêêl nambe vakasin-anjo me-omaahonôôn-ate vakasin e, nganjo Anutu-te vakasin, ond manyinja ham anêêl lohvu. Tombe Anutu-te vakasin-anju nawiing kul hôôk ham sen ham awii-having-ato ham alompayo.
\p 
\v 14 + o 2:14 Sin 17:5*Halingg-aso, ham alohvu Anutu-te hil bel-ate sen lawii-having Yesu Kalisi vu Yudiaa-to, in hamate hil oo lavu nimeen vu ham, yik nambe sen sil oote hil Yudia lawiing vu sil-ato.
\v 15 + o 2:15 Sin 2:23; 7:52*Tonde yik hil Yudiaa-ju sen silate hil layiis Omaaho Bop Yesu osin hil sen danêêl Anutu-te vakasin langaah-ambe layimb-ato, ond yik hil Yudiaa-ju lawiing nindanjeen vu hey having, tonde sil oo davu sapa hôôk mopaatôôv sen Anutu nimbaya in-ato, tombe sil dayi omaahonôôn pin paya.
\v 16 + o 2:16 Mat 23:32-33*De sil lahelin hey in nambe hey-ame naanêêl vakasin langaah vu hil vaalu sen sil-ame Yudaa-to be Anutu dôôvu sil e, om nambêênja sil oo dawiing va nipaya ngeeyaata lôôt savok la, om Anutu-te ahekalin e naatovu sil bulotin.
\s1 Pol wiingin lôôt nambe ji hil Tesalonika jesin naah
\p 
\v 17 + o 2:17 1Tes 3:10*Halingg-aso, hey havuuh ham pasivdaka, lemu hey naavingg amu, nganjo hey akangg navu ham nalohvu busin pin, tombe hey ahengg having lôôt-ambe hey oo mosalo mop lôôt in nambe hey aangge ham amem jesin naah,
\v 18 in hey oo aawiingin lôôt nambe hey anaas vu ham, le ma. De sa Pol ond soo naawiingin balon balon nambe sa naas vu ham, le ma de Saalang-ate nimeen ngeeyaata nahilin mopaatôôv in hey.
\v 19 + o 2:19 Pil 2:15-16; 4:1; 2Tes 1:4*Mak hil tana sen hey natung mengg in sil, de hey akangg vasa be hey
\p gatee hey lak in sil hôôk yate Omaaho Bop Yesu me, hôôk busin sen dukanom-ato? Yik ham-anja, ham atu heyate nôôn.
\v 20 Keen, hey naapêêlis osin hey akangg vasa lôôt in ham.
\c 3
\s1 Pol wiing Timoti la in nambe kaandu sil
\p 
\v 1 + o 3:1 Sin 17:15*Hey-ame aalohvu nambe anaas e, in mop ma, om nimeen vu hey, tombe sa kangg vu nambe mam lung-ambe soo mando Atens.
\v 2 + o 3:2 Sin 16:1-3*Om hey aawiing yiiyate halingg Timoti sen hey ahondoos naawiing Anutu-te kul-ambe hey naanêêl Kalisi-te banye nivasa langaah-ato laas vu ham, in nambe kaandu ham in ham ambiing gaving niwêêk.
\v 3 + o 3:3 Ep 3:13; 2Ti 3:12*In va nimeen sen natovu ham-anjaato ond me-biing-ambe ham galuuh damim vu Anutu le, in ham oo alak ni nambe Anutu yoo nêêl nimeen-anja lak yaningg nambe naatovu yiiy.
\v 4 + o 3:4 Sin 14:22*De bôôy sen hey oo naahen nando having ham-ato, ond hey aanêêl vu ham nambe taamusin e yale naatovu nimeen, tombe yik gêên ham alak ni lung la nambe tokak ham-anja.
\v 5 + o 3:5 Pil 2:16*Tombe sa longgpayo nimeen lôôt om same hanggin e, yik saawiing Timoti laas in nambe sa gango naambe ham awii-having niwêêk me malis, in saambe mak omaaho palapin vaha palapin ham lôôt-ambe kape ham, tombe hey aawiing heyate kul bopaata malis amu vu ham-ande nôôn ma mava?
\s1 Timoti hako banye lo-valup atombe Pol aka vasa
\p 
\v 6 + o 3:6 Sin 18:5*Gêên Timoti vuu-ja be lo-valup atombe nêêl hamate banye nivasa vu hey nambe ham awii-having Yesu de ham ahem naving omaahonôôn. Tonde nêêl having
\p nambe ham akam navu hey lôôt, osin ham ahem anivasa be ham nawiingin nambe ham angge hey amengg, yik nambe sen hey naawiingin nambe hey aangge ham-ato.
\p 
\v 7 + o 3:7 2Tes 1:4*Halingg-aso, nimeen tovu hey-ambe hey alonggpayo nimeen, lemu hey hango tombe hey alak ni nambe ham oo awii-having, tombe mem wiing-ambe hey alonggpayo ahelavis lak.
\v 8 Om sen ham akam navu Omaaho Bop niwêêk nambêênja ond samu hey-ambe hey nando nivasa.
\v 9 Hey alonggpayo nivasa lôôt in ham hôôk Anutu me, om hey naapêêlis la vu Anutu lôôt.
\v 10 Hey oo mokataangg Anutu lôôt hôôk busin-ande langaah, in nambe biing-ambe hey aangge ham amem jesin naah. Tonde ham awii-having, le vati naahen om hey e anaas kaandu ham in nambe ham ambiing gaving osin ham alompayo doos.
\s1 Pol lohak nambe Anutu taato mopaatôôv in na vu sil
\p 
\v 11 + o 3:11 2Tes 2:16*Yik hey aawiingin nambe yate Aamangg Anutu yuuh Noow yate Omaaho Bop Yesu le taato mopaatôôv-ambe hey anaas vu ham.
\v 12 Tombe Anutu biing-ambe ham ahem gaving mango-so osin ham ahem gaving hil pin naatu bopaata lôôt, naambe sen hey ahengg naving ham-ato.
\v 13 + o 3:13 Pil 1:10; 2Tes 1:7,10*Tombe Anutu le kaandu ham alompayo be nivalok jak, in vakasin ti me-nanjip vu ham hôôk yate Aamangg Anutu me dôôk busin taamusin sen yate Omaaho Bop Yesu gaving yite hil vaambuung-aso pin-ambe lanom-ato le.
\c 4
\s1 Yaambiing va nohvu Anutu ka vasa vu yiiy
\p 
\v 1 + o 4:1 2Tes 3:6*Om halingg-aso, bôôy hey taahu ham hôôk mop sen ham sapa in nambe Anutu ka vasa vu ham-ato, ond ham navu taamuyin-anja, de Omaaho Bop Yesu-te hil yiiy, om gêên hey navu kataangg ham osin hey naanêêl niwêêk vu ham nambe ham oo pasam ambiing-ambe ham taamuyin niwêêk lôôt.
\p 
\v 2 De vakasin sen hey aanêêl vu ham lak Omaaho Bop Yesu haalêê-to ond ham alak ni.
\v 3 + o 4:3 1Tes 5:23; Hiblu 10:10; 1Pi 1:16*Tonde va sen Anutu nawiingin nambe ham ambiing-ato ond yik wiingin nambe ham naatu hil anivalok, de ham anoh nanye in baayamb.
\v 4 + o 4:4 1Ko 6:13,15*Tonde Anutu wiingin nambe ham gako vêêh ti ti osin ham alompayo nivalok, tombe ham oo monambiing va nohvu sen ham oo hako ham-ato,
\v 5 + o 4:5 Saam 79:6*de ham-ame ambiing mem nôôn danje-danjeen naambe hil vaalu sen sil doosin Anutuu-to le.
\v 6 + o 4:6 Saam 94:1*Ham-ame ambiing halim-aso paya naambêênja be ham anjakin silate va le, malis lôôt, in Omaaho Bop le bu nyevahaan dukanaah va nipaya nambêênja pin, yik naambe sen hey aanêêl langaah vu ham vulôôt-ato.
\v 7 + o 4:7 2Tes 2:13-14; 1Pi 1:15-16*In Anutu me-teey yiiy in nambe yaambiing va nipaya le, nganjo teey yiiy in nambe yaambiing va nivalok.
\v 8 + o 4:8 Luk 10:16; Esi 36:27; 37:14; 2Ko 1:22*Om omaaho sen galuuh dami vu vakasin-anja ond me-haluuh dami vu omaahonôôn e, malis, nganjo haluuh dami vu Anutu sen wiing yite Vavi Vaambuung laas vu ham-ato.
\p 
\v 9 + o 4:9 Jon 13:34*Tonde vakasin sen yahengg gaving yiiy halingg-aso sen lawii-having Yesuu-to, ond same le kaavu be tatekin vu ham e, in Anutu taato vu ham lung la, tombe yik ham ahem oo naving ham nandôô-ja.
\v 10 + o 4:10 2Tes 3:4*Tonde ham ahem naving Omaaho Bop-ate hil pin lohvu taaku Makedonia doos, om halingg-aso, hey naanêêl niwêêk naah vu ham naambe ham ahem oo pasam gaving sil lôôt.
\v 11 + o 4:11 Ep 4:28; 2Tes 3:8,12*Ham naalum mando osin melaas, tonde ham oo ganggin hamate va yuuh ame, de ham namam oo biing kul in dôôvu ham naambe sen hey aanêêl bôôy-ato.
\v 12 + o 4:12 1Ko 5:12-13; Kol 4:5*Ham ambiing naambêênja ond ham-ame le naativak in vati le, tombe mem hil sen sil-ame latu Yesu-te hil-ato, ond le lanji be lanjak ni naambe ham nando nivasa.
\s1 Omaaho Bop e nom
\p 
\v 13 + o 4:13 Ep 2:12*Halingg-aso, hil sen latu Yesu-te hil-ambe layimb-ato, ond hey aawiingin nambe ham anjak va sen le naatovu hil yimbin-anjuuto ni vanuh e, in nambe ham-ame naasu in sil-ambe ham paanyêêh ham lôôt naambe hil vaalu sen me-datung mend in Anutuu-to le.
\v 14 + o 4:14 Lom 14:9; 1Ko 15:3-4,12*Yiiy naawii-having nambe Yesu yimb-ambe kandi lak laah, om yik yalak
\p ni nambe hil sen latu Yesu-te hil-ambe layimb-ato, ond
\p sil e kandi vasa dôôk, tonde Anutu le naanggiiy sil lanom gaving Yesu.
\p 
\v 15 + o 4:15 1Ko 15:51*Tombe hey naanêêl vakasin-anjo vu ham in Omaaho Bop oo nêêl langaah vu hey nambe, hôôk busin sen Omaaho Bop dukanom-ato yiiy vaalu sen yiiy naahen nando memoos-ato, ond yame le naamunggin hil vaalu sen layimb lung laa-to le, malis.
\v 16 + o 4:16 1Tes 1:10; 2Tes 1:7; 1Ko 15:52*Yik Anutu le naanêêl niwêêk atombe angela-te yêêv e naateey, tombe Anutu-te vuuk naasu, le mem Omaaho Bop vu baandoni be dukanom. Tombe hil sen latu Kalisi-te hil-ambe layimb-ato ond sil e kandi jak naamunggin,
\v 17 + o 4:17 Jon 12:26*tonde mem le gako yiiy vaalu sen yiiy naahen nando memoos-anjôôto be yanjakana bayiimb alo baandoni gaving hil vaalu sen layimb-ambe kandi lak laah-ato, tombe mem yana balup vu Omaaho Bop vu taaku vumbalaamb, in yiiy mando gaving Omaaho Bop danggata osin danggata.
\v 18 Om vakasin-anjo ham oo monaanêêl in biing-ambe halim-aso londpayo nivasa jak.
\c 5
\s1 Yiiy oo mando mengg naatum in Omaaho Bop e nom
\p 
\v 1 + o 5:1 Mat 24:36*Halingg-aso, ham-ame doosin in nambe hey kaavu kaapiya be hey naanêêl Omaaho Bop-ate busin osin ta vu ham e,
\v 2 + o 5:2 Mat 24:42-44; 2Pi 3:10; Taato 3:3*in ham oo alak ni vanuh nambe busin sen Omaaho Bop nom-ato, ond le naatovu yiiy pavis
\p naambe omaaho hôôndak ti valup hôôk busin lavuun.
\v 3 + o 5:3 Esi 13:10; Mat 24:39; Luk 21:34-35; Jon 16:21-22*Tombe hil e daanêêl naambe, “Vakasin melaas neep om yiiy nando nivasa,” tombe yik nimeen bopaata le naatovu sil pavis in nambe kawiiy sil, de sil-ame lalohvu nambe dapak in e, naambe sen vêêh noow nayêêy in navu gako tombe hango nivaane pavis.
\p 
\v 4 Om halingg-aso, ham-ame nando hôôk mekanu in nambe vaa-ju naatokak ham pavis naambe omaaho hôôndak-ato le, malis.
\v 5 + o 5:5 Lom 13:12; Ep 5:9*In ham pin atu hil amelangaah om ham nando hôôk taaku melangaah, yame hil amekanu de yiiy nando hôôk taaku mekanu le, malis.
\v 6 Om yame naanggop naambe hil vaalu le, nganjo yiiy mando mengg naatum-ande yame yalukook biing paya naambe hil sen danum bel e.
\v 7 Hil deep ond deep busin, de hil danum bel-ambe lundkook wiing paya ond danum hôôk taaku busin.
\v 8 + o 5:8 Ep 6:14,17*Nganjo yiiy nando hôôk taaku melangaah, om yiiy mando osin yalukook biing kul anivasa, de yaanggulis Anutu baambu osin yahengg gaving omaahonôôn, ond mem tu dayongg-ambe nahilin yiiy baambungg in ngaamong. De yakangg monambu Anutu le nom in nôôh yiiy vêêl-ato naatu tôômb taambusin, in nambe ngaamong naam-ato ond salosak ak tôômb-anju, be yame gangoyin naambe la hanggwang yalungg e, yik yalungg oo neep nikuusin.
\v 9 + o 5:9 1Tes 1:10; 2Tes 2:14*Anutu me-holin yiiy in nambe yite ahekalin naatovu yiiy e, nganjo holin yiiy
\p in nambe kul sen yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi wiing in nambe nôôh yiiy vêêl-ato nôôn jak vu yiiy.
\v 10 + o 5:10 Lom 14:8-9; 1Tes 4:14*In yimb
\p in nambe dôôvu yiiy, om naambe yiiy mando memoos me yaanggimb, ond yik yiiy ahondoos mando metumin gaving yi.
\v 11 + o 5:11 Jut 20*Om ham oo kaandu ham osin ham andôôvu ham in nambe ham aniwêêk jak, yik naambe sen ham nawiing-ato.
\s1 Pol samu vakasin ahus heey
\p 
\v 12 + o 5:12 1Ko 16:18; 1Ti 5:17*Halingg-aso, hey kataangg ham naambe ham anjêênin ham vu hil sen dawiing kul hôôk ham lavuun, sen Omaaho Bop holin sil-ambe latu hamate yêêv-ambe dawiing tanasin vu ham-ato.
\v 13 Ham angge sil anivasa lôôt osin ham ahem gaving sil in kul sen dawiing-ato, tombe ham mando osin vakasin melaas.
\p 
\v 14 + o 5:14 2Tes 3:6,11,15*Om halingg-aso, hey naanêêl vu ham naambe ham ambu kôôvu nitambo-so, tonde ham kaandu hil sen londpayo nimeen-ato, de ham andôôvu hil sen sil-ame lalohvu nambe sil baale niwêêk e, tonde ham naalum in hil pin-ambe ham naanêêl vakasin melaas vu sil.
\p 
\v 15 + o 5:15 Pro 20:22; Lom 12:17; 1Pi 3:9*Ham ganggin ham in nambe ham ti-te omaaho ti biing yi paya, ond me-bu nipaya dukanaah nyevahaan e, nganjo ham aniwêêk-ambe ham ambiing va nivasa mu vu mango-so de vu omaahonôôn pin.
\p 
\v 16 + o 5:16 Pil 4:4*Ham alompayo nivasa jak busin pin,
\p 
\v 17 + o 5:17 Luk 18:1; Kol 4:2*de ham oo monanohak nohvu busin pin,
\v 18 + o 5:18 Ep 5:20*tonde va pin sen naatovu ham-ato ond ham oo monaapêêlis vu Anutu, in ham atu Yesu Kalisi-te hil
\p om Anutu yoo wiingin nambe ham ambiing naambêênjo.
\p 
\v 19 + o 5:19 Ep 4:30*Ham-ame anggilin Vavi Vaambuung-ate mop e.
\p 
\v 20 + o 5:20 1Ko 14:1,39*Ham-ame angge Anutu-te vakasin sen hil danêêl langaah-ato be ham galuuh damim vu naambe va malis e,
\v 21 + o 5:21 1; Jon 4:1*nganjo ham sahi va pin-ambe va vaalu sen nivasaa-to ond ham naapuvu,
\v 22 + o 5:22 Iyop 1:1,8; 2:3*de ham oo anjakin ham nivasa lôôt in va nipaya vaha vaha pin.
\p 
\v 23 + o 5:23 Lom 15:33; 2Tes 3:16*Tonde Anutu sen nawiing-ambe yiiy nando melaas-ato, ond biing-ambe ham naatu omaahonôôn nivalok keenaanôôn, tonde ganggin ham kanum osin ham alompayo de ham anim naavi nivasa, in ham mando nivasa, de vakasin me-nanjip vu ham hôôk busin sen yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi dukanom-ato le.
\v 24 + o 5:24 1Ko 1:9; 2Tes 3:3*In Anutu sen teey ham-ato me-le gavuuh ham e, ond yoo le ganggin ham naambêênja.
\p 
\v 25 + o 5:25 Kol 4:3; 2Tes 3:1*Halingg-aso, ham akam bu hey hôôk lohakin,
\p 
\v 26 + o 5:26 Lom 16:16*tonde ham anôôh Omaaho Bop-ate hil namand jak sa haalengg.
\p 
\v 27 Sa naanêêl vu ham jak Omaaho Bop haale naambe ham naasevin kaapiyaa-jo vu Omaaho Bop-ate hil pin vuu-ja be sil gango.
\p 
\v 28 Yik vakasin lung laa-ja. Yate Omaaho Bop Yesu Kalisi-te samu samu naas mando gaving ham. 
